description: This 1 bed +den offers an amazing open floor plan with lots of natural light.  Hardwood floors, exposed brick and stainless steel appliances round out this unit. A few more perks include, in unit laundry, central AC, extra storage in the basement and a shared roof deck with water and city views.  Close to public transportation and highways, with a short walk to bars, restaurants and supermarket.
